  5,
  'top-10-chicago-neighborhoods-where-local-seo-matters-most',
  'published',
  'Top 10 Chicago Neighborhoods Where Local SEO Matters Most',
  'Not every Chicago neighborhood is the same when it comes to local search competition. This breakdown looks at 10 neighborhoods where local SEO can make a direct, measurable difference.',
  '[{"_type":"block","_key":"935c487f","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"56321f35","text":"Why Neighborhood-Level SEO Works in Chicago"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"2cb0e458","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"c781329c","text":"Chicago isn''t a monolith. It''s a city of distinct neighborhoods with their own identities, customer bases, and search behaviors."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"e5b9a7e0","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"7148ee53","text":"1. River North"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"433cbb80","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"1286bc24","text":"One of the densest commercial neighborhoods in the city and one of the highest-competition zones for local search."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"81c00a9c","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"53e82dae","text":"2. Wicker Park and Bucktown"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"9ad1a428","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"f378253c","text":"High concentration of independent retailers, restaurants, fitness studios, and creative businesses."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"cd5decb8","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"c6a2246a","text":"3. Lincoln Park"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"8497cf73","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"dd4c7741","text":"An affluent, established demographic with strong spending power."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"e1ad8b2f","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"f0557833","text":"4. Logan Square"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"075f6710","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"c6da0638","text":"Logan Square has grown into one of Chicago''s most visited neighborhoods over the past decade."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"d30f515f","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"7cbd23c7","text":"5. The Loop and West Loop"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"4444718e","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"8f01663d","text":"The Loop powers daytime searches. The West Loop has become one of the city''s premier dining destinations."}]}]',
  'Top 10 Chicago Neighborhoods for Local SEO | 2026 Guide',
  'Which Chicago neighborhoods have the highest local SEO opportunity? A practical guide for businesses targeting specific areas.',
  datetime('now')
